<p>A collection of strongly-typed constant enumerations for PHP — over 1,600 constants across 73 classes (general, HTTP, mail, JWT/JOSE, OAuth 2.0/OIDC), all sharing one reflection API through <code>ConstantsTrait</code>. No <em>magic strings</em>.</p>

